The '''Devils tower''' was a mountain on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]] shaped akin to a giant [[Volcano/Legends|volcano]]. There was a runway nearby, suggesting the location for a small [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] corps base or an emergency landing strip. This monument was the source of conjecture for many scientists throughout Naboo and was known throughout the galaxy as being a peculiar monument. Media released posters of the peak and people built models of it frequently.

